*Learn more about ZModel models in the [ZenStack documentation](https://zenstack.dev/docs/reference/zmodel/data-model).*

<details>
<summary>Declaration · <code>../../../../../tmp/zenstack-schema-0a7ab6b0-1b9c-46fb-9621-375899795d82.zmodel</code></summary>

\`\`\`prisma
/// Represents a registered user.
            model User {
                id    String @id @default(cuid())
                /// User's email address.
                email String @unique @email
                /// Display name shown in the UI.
                name  String
                role  Role
                posts Post[]

                @@allow('read', true)
                @@deny('delete', true)
                @@index([email])
                @@meta('doc:category', 'Identity')
                @@meta('doc:since', '1.0')
            }
\`\`\`

</details>

